Foot & mouth disease - Uruguay 20010425.0813
Date: Fri 27 Apr 2001 12:22:52 +0200
From: Chris Griot <Christian.Griot@ivi.admin.ch>

EMERGENCY MESSAGE FROM OIE
Date: Thu 26 Apr 2001 13:12:18 +0200
TO ALL DELEGATES TO THE OIE
FOOT AND MOUTH DISEASE IN URUGUAY
Translation of a summary of an e-mail received on 25 Apr 2001 from Dr
Carlos A. Correa Messuti, Ministry of Animal Production, Agriculture
and Fisheries, Montevideo:
Cattle showing FMD signs were detected in two farms in Soriano
department.
Samples taken from cattle were positive to VIA test. High titres of
antibodies against FMD virus type A were detected using ELISA.
Control measures: slaughter of all susceptible animals in both farms.
Ban on
movements.
--
Information Department
Office International des Epizooties (OIE)
information.dept@oie.int
........................................jw
